Maybe you could do this:
    - Force all accounts to use the trash bin
    - Modify your webskins to remove the Empty Trash Button and the=20
Delete button for the trash folder
    - Force the "On Logout Remove from Trash if Older than" setting to=20
one month
    - Tell everyone the messages in trash are removed when they are that =

old.

Nicolas

